  m_text: 'Ashes of the Fallen

    A prequel to Sylvane: Between Two Worlds


    After
    his defeat against the God of Time, Arthur is cast into the depths of the earth.
    Stripped of his power, he must fight his way back to the surface, facing deadly
    enemies and reclaiming his strength.


    His goal is clear to return and confront
    the God of Time, and finish what he started.'
